<plot>A 30-minute follow-up piece for Roger &amp; Me, this was first shown when that film was broadcast as part of the PBS series P.O.V. Moore briefly re-examines the economic collapse of Flint and the changes that have taken place in the earlier movies' major figures, from Roger Smith down to the evicted tenants, as well as collateral material about the celebrity status of himself and the film.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?430725</url></doc>
